Package: fastEmbedR
Type: Package
Title: Fast UMAP and t-SNE from Precomputed KNN Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Stefano",
    family = "User",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "stefano@example.com")
Author: Stefano User [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Stefano User <stefano@example.com>
Description: A compact UMAP and t-SNE implementation focused on fast
    embeddings from precomputed nearest-neighbor index and distance matrices.
    The graph construction, exact nearest-neighbor search, and stochastic
    layout optimization are implemented in native C++ with a user-facing API
    centered on fast KNN reuse.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/tkcaccia/fastEmbedR
